# Web Application Firewall (WAF) using Cloudflare

## 🔐 Project Overview
Implemented a Web Application Firewall using Cloudflare to protect web applications from attacks like SQL Injection, XSS, and DDoS.

## 🚀 Key Features
- Traffic filtering and monitoring
- Rule-based attack detection
- Logging and reporting
- IP blocking and rate limiting

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Cloudflare WAF
- Burp Suite
- Wireshark (optional)
- Linux

## ⚡ Attacks Detected
- SQL Injection
- Cross-Site Scripting (XSS)
- Suspicious HTTP traffic

## 📊 Results
- Successfully blocked simulated malicious requests
- Identified abnormal traffic patterns using logs

